## smtp

For STARTTLS SMTP server:
  courier.smtp.connection_uri:
  smtp://name%40maildomain.com:url_encoded_passwd@mailmydomain.corp:587/

For SMTPS server:
  courier.smtp.connection_uri:
  smtps://name%40maildomain.com:url_encoded_passwd@mailmydomain.corp:465/


